				\begin{document}$$1.75\cdot 10^{-6}$$\end{document}, but this included a particularly low coupling efficiency to the single-mode fiber (3.5·10-3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
